getValueBinding

public static javax.faces.el.ValueBinding getValueBinding(javax.el.ValueExpression ve)
Given a ValueExpression ve, return a ValueBinding. The returned ValueBinding will implement StateHolder and Serializable interfaces if ve implements these interfaces.
Parameters:
ve - The ValueExpression
Returns:
a ValueBinding equivalent to the ValueExpression
